<html>
<body>
	<p>
		Hey there <%= @user.name -%>,
	</p>
	
	<p>
		Here is your weekly friend list update!
	</p>
	
	<p>
		You had:<br /> 
		<%= pluralize(@new_friend, 'new friend') -%>.<br />
		<%= pluralize(@canceled, 'friend') -%> cancel their accounts or change their privacy settings.<br />
		<%= pluralize(@refriend, 'friend') -%> re-friend you after de-friending you.<br />
    	<%= pluralize(@reactivated, 'friend') -%> re-activate their account.<br />
		<%= pluralize(@defriend, 'friend') -%> de-friend you or you de-friended them.<br />
	</p>
	
	<p>
		If you'd like, you can take a look at your <%= link_to 'updated friend list', root_url -%>.
	</p>
	
	<%= render :partial => 'footer', :locals => {:user => @user} -%>
	
	<p>
		Thanks,<br />
		The Defriendalize Team
	</p>
</body>
</html>
